Manage pairs () [] {} "" '' etc with the sandwich plugin.

The classic plugin is tpope vim-surround.

Sandwich is the hipster modern version.

https://github.com/machakann/vim-sandwich

Add quotes around the current little word: saiw"
Add quotes around the current big word: saiW"
Delete quotes: sdb
Change single quotes to double quotes: sr'"

'test'
"test2"
